songs.title: Baguetti Jungle (Snippet)
songs.lyrics:
Oou, like a strap, let that thang pop
[?] Like the drip, like the raindrop
Chains on the streets, yeah we [?]
Watch me wipe the floor like a, mop
Blood clot, on the scope, it's a Longshot
Blood clot, it's a fire on the rooftop
Blood clots, mugshots, we don't name drop
Blood clots, dreadlocks, it's a culture shock
